WEBVTT

37:45.274 --> 37:46.483
About half an hour ago.

37:46.524 --> 37:47.608
The flight was a little delayed.

37:47.649 --> 37:49.774
Sir, this is Suresh Babu.
He used to be posted at our station.

37:50.983 --> 37:52.274
They said the DGP is in a meeting.

37:52.316 --> 37:53.358
-They will call us now.
-Sir!

37:53.483 --> 37:54.941
The meeting's over.
He's ready to see you now.

37:54.983 --> 37:56.399
-Is it? Let's go.
-Okay, sir.
